suffix = str(time.time()).replace('.', '')[-5:]
test_app = test_app = Mastodon.create_app('mastodon.py generated test app',
    api_base_url='http://localhost:3000/')
test_app_api = Mastodon(test_app[0], test_app[1], api_base_url=
    'http://localhost:3000/')
test_token = test_app_api.create_account('coolguy' + suffix, 'swordfish', 
    'email@localhost' + suffix, agreement=True)
assert test_token
pytest.mark.vcr(match_on=['path'])
